short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Turns all Facebook images into YOU!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Ever noticed how there aren't enough photos of yourself on Facebook? Well, now that can change! This extension will replace images on Facebook with your own profile image, so you can bask in your conceit.
